casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
MEDINA S255373 Supreme Court of California. JUNE 19, 2019

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

The petitions for review are granted. Further action in this matter is deferred pending consideration and disposition in a related issue in People v. Canizales, S221958 (see Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.512(d)(2) ), or pending further order of the court. Submission of additional briefing, pursuant to *824California Rules of Court, rule 8.520, is deferred pending further order of the court.
